    "description": "<p>We provide wide spectrum of civil and RC construction services . We take pride specializing in reinforced concreting works,&nbsp;general earthworks, deep excavation, shaft works, alteration and addition&nbsp;works&nbsp;and disposal of excavated foundation materials. Our current and completed in projects include works such as drainage infrastructure (small drains to box culvert drains),RC structures such as sub-stations, holding tanks ,ejector pits and permanent RC structure works. Seong Construction was founded and managed by a team of highly experienced and skilled professionals. The management team has wide ranging experiences in Public Sector projects with various authorities&nbsp; LTA, PUB, MOT, MOE, CAG and Institutional/Community projects .We also manage Private Sector Projects in Residential, Commercial, Industrial, Temporary site offices and Shipyards</p>",
